   <section>
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>We envision a world where every person has access to the nourishment they need, and where surplus food is shared rather than wasted. By fostering a community of caring individuals, businesses, and organizations, we aim to create a sustainable solution for food distribution that minimizes waste and alleviates hunger.</p>
